Title: The More You Know
Description:
This whole area is littered with Zandalari artifacts. I would be lying if I said studying them didn't interest me. I am fascinated by the significance of these objects to their rituals.

The more we understand our enemies, the better prepared we are to defeat them.

If I am to study them, I will need to see them up close. Bring me as many artifacts as you can find.
ObjectivesText: Retrieve 6 Ritual Artifacts from around Conqueror's Terrace.
RewardText: These are excellent finds! Studying them will take time, but there is much to be gained in understanding the Zandalari.
